lead_paragraph: Premier League champions Chelsea, beginning to find their form under Guus Hiddink after a shocking start to the season, will face Manchester City in the outstanding tie of the FA Cup fifth round following Sunday's draw.

headline.print_headline: Chelsea Face Man City in FA Cup Glamour Tie
